result.name: Shiro

reviews.text: Great food and dining environment! A little pricey, but worth it

This place is amazing. It’s shocking to me that it’s not more popular. Every time I go there is no wait and the sushi is the best I’ve had in Hong Kong. Their Seared Scallop with Cod Roe is absolutely to die for.
Nice services
Friendly and efficient service with tasty Japanese cuisine.
I tried the lunch bento.   Good quality Japanese food and comfortable seating.  Staff is friendly.  I would recommend you to book in advance if you want to dine here because it's usually pretty full.
